skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: big ense collection
des:
Play original enses! Play by story, user handle, latest recorded enses, and most popular enses. 

The following are some example phrases you can use. You can replace what is in the brackets. 

Alexa, ask Big Ense Collection to play a feed from [Clyde]. 
Alexa, ask Big Ense Collection to tell the story [journey to inauguration]. 
Alexa, ask Big Ense Collection to play the latest. 
Alexa, ask Big Ense Collection to play what is most popular.
